  ('medical-tech-moex-13208', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-101-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關心臟超音波的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["病患準備，無需空腹", "原則上在足夠的穿透力的前提下儘量選用較高頻的換能器（transducer），可有較好的解析能", "成年人一般使用3.5 MHz換能器，較胖的病患可能需要使用較低頻如2.25 MHz換能器", "小兒科病患通常選用1MHz的換能器"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21323ff2e228", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b5e305bfaac5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "108", "s": "0107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
