  ('medical-tech-moex-13211', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-101-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者並非B模式即時掃描（real time scan）之特性？', '["易取得動態影像", "操作方便而省時", "可獲得不同角度之影像切面", "可獲得一完整之斷面影像"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21323ff2e228", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b5e305bfaac5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "108", "s": "0107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-13212', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-101-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關超音波檢查名詞的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["增益（Gain）：超音波回音經放大器處理，放大器輸出與輸入訊號強度之比。調整增益會使所有回音弱時 變強，強時變弱", "換能器（Transducer）是利用壓電效應（Piezoelectric Effect）原理將不同能量互相轉換的裝置", "解析能（Resolution）：能分辨相鄰兩構造的能力", "時間增益補償（Time gain compensation）：又稱為深度增益補償（Depth gain compensation），補償超音 波行經組織的衰減，使影像呈像均勻"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21323ff2e228", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b5e305bfaac5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "108", "s": "0107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-13213', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-101-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種器官使用M-mode超音波檢查最多？', '["肝臟", "甲狀腺", "心臟", "肺臟"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21323ff2e228", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b5e305bfaac5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "108", "s": "0107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-13214', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-101-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關超音波的敘述，何者正確？', '["超音波遇到不同的組織會發生反射、曲折及散射現象", "在均質液體中超音波也會衰減", "骨骼本身反射強度低，超音波的穿透力差", "超音波在水中的傳導速度較空氣中慢"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "21323ff2e228", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b5e305bfaac5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "108", "s": "0107", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
